article.description: — JT Shumate had 20 points as Toledo topped Valparaiso 69-61 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Shumate scores 20 to carry Toledo over Valparaiso 69-61
article.linkText: Shumate scores 20 to carry Toledo over Valparaiso 69-61
article.story: VALPARAISO, Ind. -- — JT Shumate had 20 points as Toledo topped Valparaiso 69-61 on Tuesday night. Shumate made 4 of 6 3-pointers. He added nine rebounds. Ryan Rollins had 15 points for Toledo (1-0). Setric Millner Jr. added 10 points. RayJ Dennis had six rebounds. Thomas Kithier had 16 points for Valpo (0-1). Kevion Taylor added 12 points. Trevor Anderson had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25
